Package: scCDC
Type: Package
Title: Single-cell (-nucleus) RNA Sequencing Data Contamination
        Detection and Correction
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-06-18
Author: Yihui Cen, Weijian Wang, Zezhen Lu
Maintainer: Yihui Cen <yihui.19@intl.zju.edu.cn>
Description: This package uses entropy theory to detect contaminated genes and perform decontamination 
  process using Ostu's Method or Cumulative Distribution Function (CDF)-based Method. It offers a fast
  procedure to allow users to targets contaminations and remove them.
